race.description: Shellharbour City Motors Test Drive F&M Maiden Handicap
race.comment: TSZINSI (13) did her best work late to get up for third on debut over 1200m at this track last time out. Drawn to enjoy a lovely run and with a little natural improvement is a big chance to take this out. SEMIBREVE (2) caught the eye first-up over 1200m then wasn't suited staying at that trip last start when she closed well but missed the placings. Will be hard to hold out over a little more ground this afternoon. AURA (1) is a sparingly raced five-year-old fresh from a four-month break. Two trials should have her forward enough to run a decent race. MICHONNE'S KATANA (14) was solid here on debut without a whole lot of luck. She'll be better for that effort and she's a leading chance with natural improvement expected.
